Tlou Segolela Sports Development (TSSD), a non-profit organisation that annually stages the Tlou Segolela Annual Festive Soccer and Netball Tournament, is proud to have partnered with MSC Business College Polokwane with the aim of ensuring correlation between sport and education.
Mpho Moloto, Chief Operations Officer of TSSD said it was an honour to be partnered with the college to ensure quality education to the young sportsmen and women.
MSC Business College awarded three bursaries to deserving participants of the 2017 annual tournament.
“We are delighted to have this opportunity to maintaining our goal of developing communities through sports and developing sports in rural communities, and we look forward to the 2018 project,” Moloto concluded.
